{"hash":"fbfb38bebc12c48de74c15ffadd8468038169393","data":{"post":{"id":"5","title":"table에서 첫번째 column을 가로만 고정하고, 세로는 스크롤링되도록 하는 간단한 방법","date":"2020. 09. 23","timeToRead":2,"path":"/5/","canonical_url":true,"tags":[{"id":"css","title":"css","path":"/tag/css/"},{"id":"개발경험","title":"개발경험","path":"/tag/%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EA%B2%BD%ED%97%98/"}],"description":"css의 `position: sticky`를 이용해 table 태그의 첫번째 <td> 태그를 scoll 시 가로로만 고정되도록 하는 방법을 기록한 글입니다. 안타깝게도 IE에선 작동이 안됩니다.","content":"<p>최근에 회사 내부에서 사용하는 솔루션을 위한 웹서비스 중 table 태그를 사용한 화면구성이 필요하여 만들게 되었었습니다. 어떤 화면인지 캡쳐는 할 수 없지만 대략 구성은 아래와 같습니다.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1280 1040' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-1aaf87d068b28fdc0d8d52e9efe8f4e3'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-1aaf87d068b28fdc0d8d52e9efe8f4e3)' width='1280' height='1040' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAA0CAYAAAA62j4JAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAIQklEQVRo3uVaa09j1xX1P2oFyQAGjB/Y%2bG2YCa1mGuVDVVVRmxkCmVaJ2q/9Af0BrZIoqdSZSMnvSGZgZpJp1CHl4Qd%2b4TdgA4bVvc718VzMvRdCNNIEW9q695x91r6bc/feZy9j128jf8Od6BLuRFbwm9iKXJfxVuCPFvIeFoN/wLuxv%2bOjha9wP/Fv/Cn58Ery5yvpHpyR%2b7wmHvTWc%2b6Ls%2bsSD4wx16Qe4oPk51iOf4a/3n6Ipein%2bGjxAT68%2bQVcSf87CEY9mF9IYGExifj8HG6Mj%2bDGRE/kfsz9htyPwu0Zxa8C7%2bMvb32Je5GPRT7Bksg9kywp%2bfTcvNLJg5ein%2bBu%2bGNjnYz7870153XGPJ3XshL7DB%2bEjT/obvSf6npv7h9YjglGdEsiKzJHG8ty/z6vHItfd8XvlfjnuJ/6l9oUl2fSj%2bnpadx4cwxu96S6Bvyz8HhmMDPjhd8fwOjIKMbH3fDIOBKK4o1fujHtDmDWF4bPE0LIH0XQH0PAOydjkakgvNNB%2bGc4Dsp8GAG5n57wY0Z0kVBC6abdfsx6I/BOGWtoLxpKmnRhsRNSutFfjOHNETfGRibhnvZiJOXBzHgQt4O/x8xkEKnFu%2bJrArdmfIh7AnCP%2bxAJJpVtXmd9EdxK/RrL793H1IQPnskAvJNzcIXnopidDQjYj2AwqK6xWAyhUAjRaBSJREI2xg2v14ewjJOJGCYmxhQmkYojmUoiNZ9EIpkQict9Sq2Jx2NKv3AzpXRJkbnIHGIyv3BzXs1Fo2HMy/pYNIJY